6:
Haven't seen you around these parts. 
You new here?
10:
A-a dragon?! And you speak the 
language of humans?
14:
Well, I ain't no lizard, I can tell you that!
You can call me Faf. What's your 
name?
18:
I go by Light. I'm the champ—er, an 
adventurer, or more like a chaperone 
of sorts.
21:
Huh. I don't really get it, but that 
means you're lookin' for quests and 
stuff to take on, right?
25: That's correct. What do you know?
34:
I must ask... Are you here alone? Do 
you not have any companions?
38:
I guess I'm more of a free spirit. I can't 
restrict myself to just one party, you 
know?
40:
Not to mention the people in the guild 
officers here feed me for free!
42:
People probably think I'm supposed to 
be the guild mascot or something. 
I guess I'm just too cute for my own 
good, huh?
45:
So you've made this place a home of 
sorts.
50:
Yep! I'll take living it up here over flyin' 
out in the cold outside any day!
55:
Well, aren't you just the CUTEST widdle 
adventurer I've seen! Are you wooking 
for a widdle quest to go on?
57:
He's so FWUFFY! You just have to join 
my party! I'll make sure you're well 
taken care of, too!
66:
...That was a close one.
I must thank you for helping me again
—
70:
What's the big idea? 
You tryin' to take my spot?
73:
Listen up, buddy. You're in my house, 
so don't get cocky just because you 
have some fluffy bunny ears!
74:
Don't underestimate me just 'cuz I'm 
cute! I'm still a dragon, you know!
77:
Ahaha... I assure you, that was not my 
intention.
79:
But perhaps I should've been more 
considerate toward you, seeing as you 
are an esteemed dragon. Please allow 
me to apologize.
84:
Heh! I guess I got a little heated, but 
I'm glad SOMEONE around here knows 
how to show some respect!
88:
There you are. Dinner's ready, so 
I thought I'd check up on you. Find any 
good quests?
91:
I've hit a small snag of sorts, now that 
you mention it.
95:
...!
Aw, aren't you just a cute little thing! 
Do you live here?
99:
Yup! I guess you could say I'm the 
mascot around here! Play your cards 
right, and I might even let you pet me!
104:
Well, now that my companion is here, 
I ought to be going. Thank you once 
again for earlier.
108:
I think you're really gonna like tonight's 
dinner, Light. It might just be my 
magnum opus!
111:
Sounds like the perfect opportunity for 
us to work up an appetite with some 
questing!
115:
What's with those two? 
They're awfully chummy.
121:
H-hey! Wait up for me!
Can you take me with you?
125:
...?
I thought you were happy playing the 
mascot.
129:
Not ALL the time... Sometimes even 
I get in the mood to join a party now 
and then, you see?
130:
And all this talk of a yummy dinner got 
me hungry!
138:
Faf. Faf the dragon. Just let me handle 
this one.
144: You won't regret this, I promise!
